Level 3: The Wonder of Rowing on the Nile River

Location: Nile Bank
Background: Kobayashi arrived at the river and found that the ancient Egyptians were holding a grand ceremony to worship the river, but there was a strange sight on the water surface.

Unreasonable items:

Motorboats - Several "priests" are sailing on the Nile River.

Lifeguard (with cartoon characters) - Children wear cartoon shaped lifebuoys.

Selfie stick - Noble women holding selfie sticks to take family photos.

Plot points:
Xiaolin used the hidden microchip in the selfie stick to repair the time machine, and with a flash of light, he was once again drawn into a new era crack.
